  "title": "Procurement Coordinator #82055",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Distributor - piping</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Procurement Coordinator</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon to Fri: 9:00am to 6:00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Process daily purchase orders and track deliveries.</li><li>Update delivery schedules and shipment status records.</li><li>Source and liaise with suppliers, vendors, freight forwarders, and service providers.</li><li>Coordinate with sales and warehouse teams on goods receipt and inventory updates.</li><li>Maintain procurement documents (POs, quotations, supplier records).</li><li>Support vendor evaluation and price/cost comparisons.</li><li>Prepare and handle import/export and logistics documentation.</li><li>Ensure procurement work follows company policies and compliance requirements.</li><li>Handle ad-hoc tasks and special projects as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O-Levels.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, especially Excel.</li><li>Experience with Microsoft Dynamics NAV is a plus.</li><li>Candidates without relevant experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82055 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
